Gauteng police have confirmed he appeared in the Vereeniging Magistrates Court on Monday but the case was postponed. JOHANNESBURG Orlando Pirates player Thabo Rakhale has been arrested for allegedly assaulting his girlfriend.Gauteng police have confirmed he appeared in the Vereeniging Magistrates Court on Monday but the case was postponed.Spokesperson Fikile Funda said: The suspect Thabo Rakhale was arrested for assault in Vereeniging. He was released on bail and handed over to his lawyer. Orlando Pirates has not been available for comment.